title: honor 3 ward but was honor 4
body: I was honor 4 but i got the honor 3 ward skin. Thats not a big problem but i was wondering whats the deal with that?

replies.body: I do see the Honor 3 Ward added, but I'm not currently showing a history of you being Honor Rank 4 *during* the season. Is it possible that you might have hit rank 4 after the deadline?
